# 🌍 Wanderlust Travels — Travel Agency Landing Page  

🚀 **Live Demo:** [Click Here](https://travel-agency-project-kohl.vercel.app/)  

---

## ✨ Overview  
A modern and responsive **Travel Agency Landing Page** built with **HTML & CSS only** (no frameworks, no JavaScript).  
It features a clean, professional design, mobile responsiveness, and a fresh travel vibe.  

---

## 🔹 Features  

- 🧭 **Sticky Navbar** with smooth navigation (Home, Destinations, Packages, About, Contact)  
- 🏔 **Hero Section** with full-screen background, overlay text, and a bold CTA button  
- 🌴 **Destinations Section** showing popular travel spots with images & “Learn More” buttons  
- 💼 **Packages Section** with 3-tier pricing (Basic, Standard, Premium) — Standard plan highlighted  
- 🏢 **About Section** with agency description in a 2-column layout  
- 📬 **Contact Section** with form (Name, Email, Message) + contact info  
- 📎 **Footer** with social media links & copyright info  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used  

- **HTML5**  
- **CSS3 (Flexbox & Grid)**  
- **Google Fonts (Poppins / Open Sans)**  
- **Responsive Design with Media Queries**  

